00:29:07,375 --> 00:29:08,627
Aku yakin kau tahu itu.

364
00:29:11,588 --> 00:29:13,006
Kau benar.

365
00:29:15,008 --> 00:29:16,510
Tak bisa kulakukan sendiri.

366
00:29:17,219 --> 00:29:20,972
