PANGLIMA GITOHA
PANGLIMA DUPA

395
00:31:05,744 --> 00:31:06,578
Tak ada alasan.

396
00:31:06,661 --> 00:31:07,495
YEOLSON

397
00:31:07,579 --> 00:31:10,081
